                     <interp inst="t18141130-15-off89" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18141130-15-victim218" type="victimName">
                           Charles 
                           Griffen
                        <interp inst="t18141130-15-victim218" type="surname" value="Griffen"></interp>
