                  , about the hour of nine in the night, of the <rs id="t18141130-15-cd90" type="crimeDate">25th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18141130-15-off89 t18141130-15-cd90"></join>, and stealing therein, fifteen pencil-cases, value 2 l. 15 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18141130-15-victim220" type="victimName">
                     Charles 
                     Griffen
